query:
SELECT DISTINCT sr.hotelId, h.name, h.bookingUrl, COUNT(*) as result_count
FROM scanResults sr
JOIN hotels h ON sr.hotelId = h.id
WHERE sr.scanId = 30003
GROUP BY sr.hotelId, h.name, h.bookingUrl
